						"title": "The four pillars of secure, omnichannel retail",
						"titleSize": null,
						"subtitle": "Stop the surge in fraud, downtime, and cart abandonment. Discover the four critical pillars retailers must address now to ensure operational resilience and turn peak traffic into profit.",
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "With 60% of consumers abandoning purchases due to poor experiences and fraud attempts jumping 200% during Black Friday/Cyber Monday 2024, retailers need more than traffic. They need a secure, high-performance platform that converts visitors into loyal customers..\n\n__How Cloudflare supports maximizing holiday sales while securing your digital and physical presence:__\n\n<ul>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Optimize Performance:</strong>\nAbsorb massive traffic surges and prevent the $287M cost of downtime with cloud-scale operational resilience.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Protect Against Fraud:</strong>\nImplement a proactive, unified security posture to defend customer-facing apps against fraud and emerging AI-driven threats.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Secure Sensitive Data:</strong>\nAdopt a phased Zero Trust approach, including AI-powered email security and ZTNA, to protect valuable customer and supplier data.\n  </li>\n  <li style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0;\"><strong>Upgrade Omnichannel: </strong>\nLeverage a connectivity cloud to securely and instantly bridge legacy systems with next-gen AI and real-time engagement.\n  </li>\n</ul>\n",
